{"tid":455960,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入]懷疑中床蝨 求救","createTime":"2017-11-02T14:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T03:36:39.000Z","uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24f3ba1c4ca069c76b3a0e0a743d8480c2b46fca","tid":455960,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745a49545c167b752ecbf8ef830c0a10dec2e739","tid":455960,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864619d878519fbe8aaaacd59a59aa19ac30a53b","tid":455960,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"蝨咬應該係連續幾點好似蚊咬咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9facfd495a5fdfc6c772b2dec04965f0090392ac","tid":455960,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"有蝨咬仲訓落床 我係你就訓廳"},{"pid":"d0bb91b2696166c1e5648249d0e7bcd611793fce","tid":455960,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有蝨咬仲訓落床 我係你就訓廳</blockquote><br />\n俾屋企人搶左"},{"pid":"5048f43876bfd484b62d939c0873331ddfe2d796","tid":455960,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"張床掉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26273f02ed8ce6c06e69397513d0e399434ce49","tid":455960,"uid":73741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b56f902cacfcf87b38c8b5ef4a183a37ea16ef","tid":455960,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:35:53.000Z","msg":"如有竹隻,先用熱水浸/掉左佢(床蟲好愛呢埋向竹隻D洞到)<br />\n用蒸氣槍噴全床,都要焗一次<br />\n被&amp;床單個D要洗<br />\n翻起床板,尤其是洞洞啦啦,角頭位,用濃滴露噴,一定要噴足夠,噴到濕<br />\n之後灑天然DE粉(一定要天然,不能人造個種,否則無效)<br />\n四隻床腳用膠紙完整地痴一圈<br />\n<br />\n2星期後,以上步驟重覆一次<br />\n<br />\n床上準一次電筒&amp;紙巾<br />\n訓覺時有床蟲出現即打及清理<br />\n床上如有雜物,請放在膠箱中放在冰格雪24小時殺蟲或掉(如果你唔要/冇用的)"},{"pid":"850ede2365eb56acbb5eb4840a72d8b597334495","tid":455960,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"天然DE粉要曬到足<br />\n成張床板都有要<br />\n用黎防止佢返黎/再黎"}]}